# VHS tape — real Playwright vs lad comparison, live.
# Render: cd demo && vhs compare.tape

Output compare.gif
Output compare.mp4
Output compare.webm

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 780
Set Padding 30
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Sleep 700ms
Type "./compare.sh http://localhost:8787/pages/twitter-profile.html"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 18s
